snippet: A fight among about 200 migrants trying to get to Britain from the northern French port city of Calais left seven people injured on Saturday.
abstract: Seven people are injured after fight breaks out among 200 migrants trying to get to Britain from Calais, France.
lead_paragraph: A fight among about 200 migrants trying to get to Britain from the northern French port city of Calais left seven people injured on Saturday.

headline.main: France: Migrants Injured in Calais Brawl
